name: New Tag should be visible on post settings

elements.name: New Tag should be visible on post settings

steps.name: I enter "<ADMIN_USER>" into input field having css selector "input[name='identification']"
I enter "<ADMIN_PASSWORD>" into input field having css selector "input[name='password']"
I click on element having css selector "button.login"
I click on element having css selector "a[href='#/tags/']"
I click on element having css selector "a[href*='tags/new']"
I enter "$name_1" into input field having css selector "input[name='name']"
I click on element with xpath "//button[@type='button' and contains(., 'Save')]"
I click on element having css selector "a[href='#/posts/']"
I click on element having css selector "a[href='#/editor/post/']"
I click on element having css selector "button.post-settings"
I click on element having css selector "label[for='tag-input']+div"
I check for "$$name_1" to exist in tag selector
